# SSH hostnames the agent VM may reach via `git clone git@host:...` and
# similar. The agent's SSH client is configured (in home.nix) to tunnel
# through the firewall via HTTP CONNECT, so mitmproxy's addon checks the
# CONNECT host:22 against this host-glob list. Git-over-SSH cannot be
# scoped to individual repositories because the firewall cannot see inside
# the encrypted SSH session.

github.com
gitlab.com
bitbucket.org
ssh.dev.azure.com
